11.title: Episode #5.11
11.plot: Scientists Maggie Aderin-Pocock and Miranda Krestovnikoff embark on a quest to unearth collectibles in South Wales and southwest England that they can then sell at auction in Clevedon in Somerset.

12.title: Episode #5.12
12.plot: Television presenters and friends Angellica Bell and Jenni Falconer shop around in Surrey, Oxfordshire and Berkshire for items which they think will turn a profit when auctioned in Tonbridge in Kent.

13.title: Episode #5.13
13.plot: Actors Nigel Planer and Sally Phillips, take on the treasure-hunting challenge. The pair are joined by experts Margie Cooper and David Harper as they visit Oxfordshire, Somerset and Gloucestershire before an auction in London.

14.title: Episode #5.14
14.plot: Comedian Hardeep Singh Kohli and comedy actress Helen Lederer embark on a cross-country hunt for hidden gems that they can then sell at auction.

15.title: Episode #5.15
15.plot: Legendary Radio 2 DJs Johnnie Walker and "Whispering" Bob Harris are the celebrities taking part in the antique-hunting challenge. They travel around Devon, Somerset and Dorset before heading to auction in Salisbury.
